We are on a mission to build a remote and sustainable user acquisition agency and platform servicing innovative mobile app clients. Next to working with cutting-edge start-ups and providing a unique solutions-based product ourselves, we also have a manifesto for redistributing a portion of our profits. By committing 7% of our annual revenue to help fight the global ecological crisis and human inequality, we hope to inspire others in the industry to make similar commitments. To enact positive global change tech companies and corporate citizens alike will need to mature and think beyond profits. People in this sector must think creatively about playing their part in improving life on earth for all living beings. In this respect, leads by example.

